0: Not disabled
1: Sample and hold disabled and stable		 RO 0

This flag is valid immediately after the operation setting it (FMSTAT.BUSY is delayed some cycles)
0 : Not busy
1 : Busy		 RO 0
0 POWER_MODE Power state of the flash sub-system.
0 : Active
1 : Low power		 RO 0
